OL,3,CWoman who thinks her drink was spiked
OL,4,C'feared for her life' after collapsing
OL,6,FSimone told ITV News' Imogen McGuckin
OL,7,Fshe wants to warn others about spiking.
OL,9,FA woman who thinks her drink was
OL,10,Fspiked in Bristol says she "feared for
OL,11,Fher life" after collapsing and
OL,12,Fsuffering seizures.
OL,14,FSimone White, 43, had been enjoying a
OL,15,Fprosecco brunch with her friend at a
OL,16,Fvenue in the city centre on Saturday 4
OL,17,FMay. Five weeks later, she's still not
OL,18,Fback to normal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
