OL,3,CWoman who thinks her drink was spiked
OL,4,C'feared for her life' after collapsing
OL,6,FThe night began normally, but after
OL,7,Fbeing in the venue for two hours
OL,8,FSimone started feeling unwell.
OL,10,FShe said: "I started to feel very
OL,11,Ffunny -a bit too drunk and unaware of
OL,12,Fthings that were going on. I just felt
OL,13,Flike I'd had a bit too much to drink
OL,14,Ftoo quickly."
OL,16,F"I thought 'I'll go and sit outside
OL,17,Ffor a bit and get some fresh air'. I
OL,18,Fremember sitting down and thinking
OL,19,F'something's really not right'."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
