OL,6,FIf you have been affected by any of
OL,7,Fthe issues raised in this report,
OL,8,Fthere is help available to you. Visit
OL,9,Fthe charity for support, resources and
OL,10,Fguidance. If you believe you have been
OL,11,Fa victim of crime, contact your local
OL,12,Fpolice force to report it.
OL,14,FSimone thinks she then tried to make
OL,15,Fher way to the bus stop at the Bay
OL,16,FHorse, as she remembers walking down
OL,17,FSt Nicholas Street.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
