OL,3,CWoman who thinks her drink was spiked
OL,4,C'feared for her life' after collapsing
OL,6,F"I remember seeing the cobbles on the
OL,7,Ffloor and then I looked down the road
OL,8,Fand it was like a tunnel. Everything
OL,9,Fwas all blurry and spinning.
OL,11,F"At that point, I think I'd probably
OL,12,Fstarted to hallucinate maybe," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FShe collapsed near Bristol Bridge,
OL,16,Fwhere some passersby found her and
OL,17,Fmanaged to call her parents and
OL,18,Fpartner George.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
