OL,4,C'feared for her life' after collapsing
OL,6,FThey took her to Southmead Hospital,
OL,7,Fwhere she spent 10 hours in the
OL,8,Femergency department, passing in and
OL,9,Fout of conscientiousness.
OL,11,FShe said: "I was gurning, screaming,
OL,12,Fclawing at the sick bowls they were
OL,13,Fgiving me, tearing them to pieces. At
OL,14,F7am I was discharged and I could
OL,15,Fbarely walk or talk at that point."
OL,17,FIn the five weeks since then, she has
OL,18,Freturned to Southmead Hospital for CT
OL,19,Fand MRI scans - and a lumbar puncture
OL,20,Fto test her cerebral fluid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
