OL,6,FThe doctors think she may have
OL,7,Fsuffered a functional neurological
OL,8,Fdisorder (FND) in reaction to whatever
OL,9,Fdrug was in her system.
OL,11,FIt occurs when someone experiences a
OL,12,Ftraumatic or stressful event, which
OL,13,Fcauses the brain's "software" to
OL,14,Fmalfunction.
OL,16,FSymptoms include muscle weakness,
OL,17,Fspeech problems, tremors and seizures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
