OL,3,CWoman who thinks her drink was spiked
OL,4,C'feared for her life' after collapsing
OL,6,F"But at the time I was really scared.
OL,7,FGenuinely fearful for my life, at one
OL,8,Fpoint.
OL,10,F"And in some ways I'm think I'm glad I
OL,11,Fdon't remember what went on, because
OL,12,Fif I was the way that I was for as
OL,13,Flong as I was, it must have been
OL,14,Fhorrendous for people to see," Simone
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FShe added: "This person, whoever it
OL,18,Fwas, had no thought about the knock-on
OL,19,Feffects that happened. It's not just
OL,20,Fthe victim it affects, it's everybody
OL,21,Faround them, everybody that loves them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
