OL,3,CWoman who thinks her drink was spiked
OL,4,C'feared for her life' after collapsing
OL,6,F"I think that's why I've been so
OL,7,Fpublic about this, because I want
OL,8,Fpeople to see what can happen. Be
OL,9,Faware of how dangerous it can be.
OL,11,F"At the end of the day, I'm a mum,
OL,12,FI've got kids. I know so many parents
OL,13,Fwith children, young adults, I don't
OL,14,Fwant this to happen to anybody else.
OL,15,FIt was just horrendous."
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Police said they
OL,18,Fwere investigating what happened to
OL,19,FSimone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
