OL,6,FA spokesman said: "We're investigating
OL,7,Fan incident in which a woman required
OL,8,Fhospital treatment in a suspected
OL,9,Fspiking incident while visiting a bar
OL,10,Fin Bristol.
OL,12,F"She had been with a group of friends
OL,13,Fin Bristol city centre between 4pm and
OL,14,F6pm on Saturday 4 May before falling
OL,15,Funwell and being taken to hospital.
OL,17,F"The incident was reported to police
OL,18,Flater that evening and enquiries are
OL,19,Fongoing. If you have any information
OL,20,Fplease call 101 and quote reference
OL,21,F5224114366."
